thread.title: Lowina Blackman

author: Lowina Blackman
title: Lowina Blackman
text:
Flashbay has a wide range of custom USB products, I wasn't sure which one to choose from, Alex sent me a big sample pack so I can touch & feel.
Account manager Alex follow up my order from design to PDF proof approval to delivery, friendly and professional.
Delivery: Fast turn around and packed safety in a big box, courier to my office.
Excellence quality of USB, all custom engraved and individually in a magnetic box, exactly how I wanted.
Highly recommend Flashbay to anyone.
